.TH FOW-SHOW 1 "31 July 2016" "Fow manual" "fow show"
.SH NAME
show \- reporting for processing steps 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Processing steps are stored in the subfolder 00_INBOX, 01_IMPORT and 02_PROCESS.With show, a summary or report can be printed.
.SH SYNOPSIS	
.TP
show [in|inbox|import|task] [options]
.TP
show tasks [options]
The first usage type reports of corresponding directory for inbox (00_INBOX), import (01_IMPORT) or both together ('in') or for the actual task in 02_PROCESS/folder/task. Default is task. 
The second usage type reports of all existing tasks in 02_PROCESS.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\-\-short, \-s
Just a summary instead of reporting every image. 
